  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Summarizing Dev Server Status**\n\nThe dev server restarted without any issues, a seamless build! Now I\'m focusing on summarizing the work, specifically aiming for clarity and conciseness in Turkish, keeping a professional and friendly tone in mind. I want to ensure the summary adheres perfectly to communication guidelines.\n\n\n"
    modified_response: "Arkada\305\237\304\261n\304\261zla tamamen **u\303\247tan uca \305\237ifreli (E2EE)**, h\304\261zl\304\261 ve son derece g\303\274venli bir \305\237ekilde mesajla\305\237abilece\304\237iniz **Kripto Sohbet** platformunu haz\304\261rlad\304\261m.\n\n### \360\237\233\241\357\270\217 \303\226ne \303\207\304\261kan \303\226zellikler\n\n- **U\303\247tan Uca \305\236ifreleme (E2EE)**: Mesajlar\304\261n\304\261z taray\304\261c\304\261dan \303\247\304\261kmadan \303\266nce end\303\274stri standard\304\261 **AES-GCM (256-bit)** algoritmas\304\261yla \305\237ifrelenir. Sunucuya yaln\304\261zca okunamaz anlams\304\261z metinler (`ciphertext`) ve ba\305\237latma vekt\303\266rleri (`IV`) iletilir. Sunucu dahil hi\303\247 kimse ortak \305\237ifrenizi bilmeden mesajlar\304\261n\304\261z\304\261 okuyamaz.\n- **Ger\303\247ek Zamanl\304\261 \304\260leti\305\237im (SSE)**: Express backend \303\274zerinde kurulan hafif ve g\303\274venilir *Server-Sent Events (SSE)* teknolojisi sayesinde mesajlar milisaniyeler i\303\247inde t\303\274m ba\304\237l\304\261 cihazlara an\304\261nda iletilir.\n- **H\304\261zl\304\261 Davet Linki**: Bulundu\304\237unuz odan\304\261n ad\304\261n\304\261 ve \305\237ifreleme anahtar\304\261n\304\261 i\303\247eren \303\266zel bir URL \303\274reterek arkada\305\237\304\261n\304\261zla payla\305\237abilirsiniz. Arkada\305\237\304\261n\304\261z linke t\304\261klad\304\261\304\237\304\261nda hi\303\247bir ayarla u\304\237ra\305\237madan do\304\237rudan \305\237ifreli odaya giri\305\237 yapar.\n- **Kriptografik Detay G\303\266r\303\274nt\303\274leyici**: Her mesaj\304\261n alt\304\261nda bulunan \"Kripto Detay\" butonuna t\304\261klayarak mesaj\304\261n \305\237ifrelenmi\305\237 ham halini (`base64 ciphertext`), `IV` parametresini ve b\303\274t\303\274nl\303\274k do\304\237rulama etiketini inceleyebilirsiniz.\n- **Kendi Kendini \304\260mha Eden Odalar**: Panelde bulunan \"Ge\303\247mi\305\237i Sil\" butonuyla odadaki t\303\274m mesaj ge\303\247mi\305\237ini sunucudan ve ba\304\237l\304\261 istemcilerden kal\304\261c\304\261 olarak tek t\304\261kla silebilirsiniz.\n\nUygulama ba\305\237ar\304\261yla derlendi ve geli\305\237tirici sunucusu \303\274zerinde yay\304\261na al\304\261nd\304\261. Arkada\305\237\304\261n\304\261zla hemen \305\237ifreli odan\304\261z\304\261 olu\305\237turup g\303\274venli mesajla\305\237man\304\261n keyfini \303\247\304\261karabilirsiniz!"
